{"id":511141,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":7,"day":4}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"庆祝中国共产党诞生五十周年征文选刊,党的光辉照千秋","genre":"","count":"141","ytitle":"","mtitle":"火红战旗传万代","ftitle":"","authors":["邵金城"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“南京路上好八连”指导员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邵金城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖上空一声雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫大地乌云开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝口南湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的恩情深似海。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光照天地五十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗风斗雨斗狼豺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝口南湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干劲滚滚来!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的光辉照千秋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红战旗传万代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝口南湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杆子打出新世界。"}]}